    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Section 2 - Error Handler (Error Workflow)\n\nOwned By: Gary Safin\nLast Updated: 20260705\n\nError workflow that captures failures from linked workflows and\nreports error details to the Academy endpoint.\n\n## Trigger\n- Error Trigger: Fires when a linked workflow fails in production\n\n## Data Captured\n- workflow.name: Name of failed workflow\n- workflow.id: Workflow ID\n- execution.url: Link to failed execution\n- execution.error.message: Error details\n- execution.lastNodeExecuted: Node that failed\n\n## Endpoint\n- POST /webhook/course/n8n103/error-report\n\n## Requirements\n- Must be published to be used as an error workflow\n- Only triggers on production executions, not manual tests\n\nPart of: n8n Foundations Program, N8N103 Course, Section 2",
        "height": 480,
        "width": 512
      },
